{"tid":235638,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聯合醫院涉醫療失誤 致鄧桂思肝衰竭","createTime":"2017-05-09T07:08:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-09T17:42:04.000Z","uid":41404,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f1bc3a4bbf676a15b1553c2608e0ecff1bbe67c2","tid":235638,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T07:08:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170509/56670712\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170509%2F56670712&d=tgCcTb3Ji4LFIEkqsM1g5rDFWuQMdHqkD4FeOi%2BWxPk%3D&h=21575009\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170509%2F56670712&h=cda87edb\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170509/56670712</a><br />\n鄧桂思早前因肝衰竭急需換肝，其女兒更因未達合法年齡未能捐肝，幸最終獲有心人捐出肝臟保命，但暫仍命危。據悉，經歷兩次換肝的鄧桂思，出現肝衰竭原因是因聯合醫院疑失誤。據悉，原是乙型肝炎帶菌者的鄧桂思也有腎病，因出現腎小球炎到聯合醫院求診，聯合醫院處方俗稱肥仔藥的類固醇，但沒有同時處方肝炎藥。因單用類固醇令她體內的乙肝病毒爆發，導致肝衰竭要換肝。聯合醫院已向鄧桂思女兒交代事件及致歉，院方今午4時將召開記者會，料講及事件。"},{"pid":"70ff6bea61e5d276883b81a21df315c4a33d36db","tid":235638,"uid":53672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T07:11:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56a2b32514198ef7e273202c89f713aaa6010f57","tid":235638,"uid":10635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T07:12:17.000Z","msg":"積下口德啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbad55a8fc90d75150bacab7ae7707f7104ea635","tid":235638,"uid":39698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T07:13:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9098ff49cdf6f60242cc7b7b331b71ac8033c7d","tid":235638,"uid":6752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T07:13:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>積下口德啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></bloc